{"tid":1757694,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(華盛頓郵報)  中共官員支持Trump連任, 不希望民主黨上台執政","createTime":"2019-11-26T15:58:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T01:06:46.000Z","uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a2bea46c58c077b5e3105ced8391d43b5fbce5b6","tid":1757694,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:58:16.000Z","msg":"北京內部人士 : Donald Trump的政治觀念, 並非與中共對立, 起碼唔會借人權問題大做文章.<br />\n<br />\n另一北京政壇中人 : 我們(中共)寧願Donald Trump連任, 不太希望民主黨上台執政. &nbsp;Donald Trump是一位生意人; 我們跟他的分歧, 用金錢便可以解決.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia-pacific/china-hopes-trump-will-be-reelected-hes-easy-to-read/2019/11/26/70538d98-00ca-11ea-8341-cc3dce52e7de_story.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2Fasia-pacific%2Fchina-hopes-trump-will-be-reelected-hes-easy-to-read%2F2019%2F11%2F26%2F70538d98-00ca-11ea-8341-cc3dce52e7de_story.html&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx9w1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=494d0888\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia-pacific/china-hopes-trump-will-be-reelected-hes-easy-to-read/2019/11/26/70538d98-00ca-11ea-8341-cc3dce52e7de_story.html</a><br />\n<br />\nChina hopes Trump will be reelected: He&rsquo;s easy to read<br />\n<br />\nBy Anna Fifield <br />\nNovember 26, 2019 at 10:51 p.m. GMT+8<br />\n........<br />\nChinese officials are betting that Trump&rsquo;s transactional approach to politics might be preferable to a more principle-driven president, whether Democrat or Republican.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Trump is a businessman. We can just pay him money and the problems will be solved,&rdquo; said a politically connected person in Beijing, speaking on the condition of anonymity to talk frankly about sensitive international issues. <strong>&ldquo;As long as we have money, we can buy him. That&rsquo;s the reason why we prefer him to Democrats.&rdquo;</strong><br />\n.....<br />\n&ldquo;Trump isn&rsquo;t ideologically opposed to China. He doesn&rsquo;t go on about human rights and Xinjiang and the South China Sea,&rdquo; the Beijing insider said, referring to China&rsquo;s contested maritime claims and to its northwestern region where authorities have detained a million Muslims."},{"pid":"7b7d6cc47c9a83b756ca9fb12c832179f4eea54c","tid":1757694,"uid":134071,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:59:11.000Z","msg":"Donald Trump怏D簽香港人權法, 證明班共官錯撚哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93a23c206d9e2f5d3266e2a384491e03fa00ca13","tid":1757694,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:59:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"798b8db5d07b714b52506c317cfdbeb9c5a8c6f8","tid":1757694,"uid":36086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7b7d6cc47c9a83b756ca9fb12c832179f4eea54c","tid":1757694,"uid":134071,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:59:11.000Z","msg":"Donald Trump怏D簽香港人權法, 證明班共官錯撚哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/haUAObs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhaUAObs.jpg&h=b5baae53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【感謝美國保護香港大遊行】</span></span></strong><br />\n【Expressing gratitude to USA for protecting Hong Kong】<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">遊行目的：感謝特朗普總統、美國國會以及美國人民支持通過香港人權及民主法案</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: l